nodes.text: Star Wars Galactic Outpost is a store operated by Disney that focus on selling Star Wars merchandise, including souvenirs, clothing and toys—many that are exclusive to Disney Parks. This includes some items previously only available at Star Wars: Galaxy's Edge.

The store is located at Walt Disney World in Florida, in the West Side area of Disney Springs. It opened on December 15th, 2015, replacing a Disney store called D Street. A similar store called Star Wars Trading Post can be found in Disney Springs' Marketplace section.
